So in the middle
segment I'm going

00:00:56.370 --> 00:00:59.350
to put an equilateral triangle.

00:00:59.350 --> 00:01:01.950
So I'm going to do it for
every one of the sides.

00:01:01.950 --> 00:01:05.600
So let me do it right there.

00:01:05.600 --> 00:01:06.760
And then right there.

00:01:06.760 --> 00:01:10.030
I think you get the idea,
