00:06:49.290 --> 00:06:52.070
Even though you can add these
bumps an infinite number

00:06:52.070 --> 00:06:53.050
of times.

00:06:53.050 --> 00:06:55.057
So a bunch of really
cool things here.

00:06:55.057 --> 00:06:55.890
One, it's a fractal.

