This is a very abstract thing.

00:07:07.590 --> 00:07:10.510
Things like this don't actually
exist in the real world.

00:07:10.510 --> 00:07:12.850
And there's a fun
thought experiment

00:07:12.850 --> 00:07:14.880
that people talk about
in the fractal world,

00:07:14.880 --> 00:07:17.540
and that's finding the
